9#ifndef DHCP_H
10#define DHCP_H
11
12#include <netinet/ip.h>
13#if __FAVOR_BSD
14#include <netinet/udp.h>
15#else
16#define __FAVOR_BSD 1
17#include <netinet/udp.h>
18#undef __FAVOR_BSD
19#endif
20
21#define DHCP_SERVER_PORT 67
22#define DHCP_CLIENT_PORT 68
23
24struct dhcp_data {
25 u8 op;
26 u8 htype;
27 u8 hlen;
28 u8 hops;
29 be32 xid;
30 be16 secs;
31 be16 flags;
32 be32 client_ip;
33 be32 your_ip;
34 be32 server_ip;
35 be32 relay_ip;
36 u8 hw_addr[16];
37 u8 serv_name[64];
38 u8 boot_file[128];
39} STRUCT_PACKED;
40
41struct bootp_pkt {
42 struct iphdr iph;
43 struct udphdr udph;
44 u8 op;
45 u8 htype;
46 u8 hlen;
47 u8 hops;
48 be32 xid;
49 be16 secs;
50 be16 flags;
51 be32 client_ip;
52 be32 your_ip;
53 be32 server_ip;
54 be32 relay_ip;
55 u8 hw_addr[16];
56 u8 serv_name[64];
57 u8 boot_file[128];
58 u8 exten[312];
59} STRUCT_PACKED;
60
61#define DHCP_MAGIC 0x63825363
